condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Enhance accounting software | Description :No later than sixty (60) days following the Effective Date, theBorrower shall ensure that the PMU has acquired operational accounting software for project accounting and financial reporting,acceptable to the Bank. | Due Date :01-Sep-2015

Finance Agreement :Establish and maintain a Project Steering Committee | Description :The Borrower shall establish and thereaftermaintain throughout project implementation a Project Steering Committee with composition, functions and responsibilities,acceptable to the Bank. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :Hire key PMU staff | Description :Notwithstanding the provisions of Section I. A.3. of Schedule 2 to the LoanAgreement, no later than forty-five days (45) from the Effective Date, the Borrower, through MHSD, shall hire the projectcoordinator, financial management specialist, at least one procurement specialist, and the accountant for the PMU. | Due Date:14-Aug-2015

Finance Agreement :Maintain the Skills and Jobs Working Group | Description :The Borrower shall maintain throughout projectimplementation, a Skills and Jobs Working Group, satisfactory to the Bank, in charge of national inter-ministerial/agencycoordination in respect of the project. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS
